claim.claim-text:
A solar cell module, comprising:
a solar cell;
a sealing member for having the solar cell embedded;
a front surface protection member; and
a back surface protection member,
wherein the back surface protection member includes a plate-like structure (a) including a fibrous reinforcement material with a thickness of 6 mm or less and with a mean linear expansion coefficient of 40 ppm/°C or less at a temperature of 20 to 25°C, and the front surface protection member includes a plate-like structure (b) including a light-transmitting resin material with a thickness of 0.03 mm or more and 0.6 mm or less.
